          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/375__step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong>&nbsp;<strong>aubergine</strong>, <strong>onion quarters </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges</strong> to a baking tray (use tin foil to avoid mess!)</p>\r\n<p>Drizzle&nbsp;with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put them in the oven for 25 min or until the vegetables are tender and coloured</p>",
